    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine runs silently and powerfully, and every feature, from the electronics to the climate control, functions exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-quality example that has been meticulously cared for and stored in a climate-controlled environment.",
